{"tid":324910,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"我發現科大附近一棵竹都冇","createTime":"2017-07-16T21:16:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T12:14:49.000Z","uid":36383,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e67a34311b2ec4b18c8a8f2dd64167833cbcd037","tid":324910,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T21:16:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解唔試下種返啲，再睇幾多日之後唔見？"},{"pid":"9dcc91e25d758fa48faf88de83e68df5a8ccc677","tid":324910,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T21:50:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc122c8252dce4079f98db36861c61d4c0ebd2a","tid":324910,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T00:37:50.000Z","msg":"又鞭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86327dbe833d4069d73282cea3dce8c8b60f7d07","tid":324910,"uid":51748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T01:01:11.000Z","msg":"咁先夠熱誠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15c8e1adee410edf501a0dafc4c22763741e9eaa","tid":324910,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T06:54:58.000Z","msg":"2015年10月6日(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】三名香港科技大學男生，聲稱要用竹竿製作旗幟作為學校活動用途，昨凌晨竟在校舍附近的地盤就地取材，由其中一男生攀過圍板潛入欲捧走竹竿，卻被地盤南亞裔保安員聽到異聲揭發。保安員窮追百米外截停三人，警員接報到場以企圖地盤盜竊罪名拘捕三人。<br />\n<br />\n稱為搞學校活動<br />\n<br />\n被捕三名科大男學生，分別姓曾（18歲）、姓祈（18歲）及姓林（19歲），三人同為科大化學學會幹事，住學生宿舍。據悉，學會近日舉辦活動，須用竹竿作旗幟，有人竟想到「信手拈來」。昨凌晨零時許，三男生走至距宿舍僅300米外的大埔仔村一個興建中的住宅地盤，其中姓曾男生攀過圍板潛入地盤內取起竹竿，祈與林則在外圍「把風」，卻被28歲南亞裔地盤保安聽到異聲揭發及報警。三人見事敗拔足狂奔，被保安員窮追百米截停，警員趕至調查，有人報稱要用竹竿製作活動用的旗幟，三人被捕帶署。科技大學回覆查詢時表示正了解事件，如有需要，大學會向學生提供適切協助。"},{"pid":"716c56b22ac03004afa34492a3883004664d8318","tid":324910,"uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T06:56:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁先夠熱誠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就連個官都比科大生嘅熱誠感動<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】三名科技大學宿生為製作所屬學會旗杆，上月5日凌晨潛入宿舍附近一個建築地盤，企圖偷取地盤的竹枝，遭保安發現報警。三人原被控企圖盜竊罪，案件昨在觀塘法院再提訊時，控方撤銷控罪，准各人自簽2,000元守行為兩年，並繳付500元訟費。<br />\n案情指，被告曾淇源（19歲）、祁晧庭（18歲）及林梓豐（19歲）於10月5日凌晨，帶備電筒到清水灣宿舍附近一個地盤，曾淇源成功潛入，其餘兩人則在閘外把風。地盤保安發現大閘有電筒光生疑，當場撞破事件。三人事敗拔足狂奔，但仍被保安截停拘捕。"},{"pid":"d8142a6ad308e3251c0f09f9269874cdd059ecc8","tid":324910,"uid":13704,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T07:10:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3bb8b8516a53f093bb8691cfb22477386f97c16c","tid":324910,"uid":41742,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T07:14:20.000Z","msg":"一失竹成千古恨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4e3e2eebf7a7677ccd7e8181e3b3e3bfcb4d2f3","tid":324910,"uid":53377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T07:25:37.000Z","msg":"科大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 竹soc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"769db6e1159440351ef0631f0b37857c15fcd0a3","tid":324910,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T07:59:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一失竹成千古恨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />頂你"},{"pid":"76d38e704a50d336b2b27afe7a6dfb73744dbc66","tid":324910,"ui